room_title: Escape room "The Dueling Room: FBI vs CIA" by IRL Escape in Minneapolis - St. Paul
room_description: The Federal Government has an extra 80 million dollars to give out to either the FBI or the CIA. No one can decide who is deserving of the extra funding so they enlisted IRL Escape to help settle the score. Who is going to get the funding? Come play a dueling room to help determine who is the most deserving agency!
